    "en": {
      "description": {
        "text": "=General= The area is pleasantly situated on a south-facing slope, about 100 metres from the road. Open, with sparse woodland. Easy to reach and dries out quickly in spring. =Directions= Take road 363 to Långviksvallen. Turn left towards Kassjö. After about three kilometres, turn right towards Storhäggsjö. Drive for about 2 km and park at the second gravel pit. Walk uphill to the right. =Sectors=",
